WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 15=

01:49.030 --> 01:49.870
Father,

01:50.670 --> 01:52.060
did you keep me away all these years

01:52.830 --> 01:54.110
for that evil spirit?

01:55.670 --> 01:57.270
All my siblings died young.

01:57.670 --> 01:58.860
You knew the reason all along.

01:59.270 --> 02:00.300
Since you knew that,

02:00.860 --> 02:02.420
why keep dealing with the evil spirit?

02:02.910 --> 02:03.750
It's all to satisfy

02:03.750 --> 02:04.830
your own desires.

02:06.390 --> 02:07.230
Father,

02:08.070 --> 02:09.550
how could you keep doing this?

02:09.950 --> 02:10.990
Driven by the evil spirit,

02:11.420 --> 02:13.070
you didn't even care that your kids

02:13.070 --> 02:13.910
were devoured by it.

02:16.390 --> 02:17.460
I am your father.

02:18.070 --> 02:19.336
Who do you think I did this for?

02:20.740 --> 02:22.020
In the Royal Court,

02:22.790 --> 02:24.070
we were always looked down on,

02:24.390 --> 02:25.620
so we were driven here.

02:26.460 --> 02:28.300
If I had not bargained
with that evil spirit,

02:29.270 --> 02:31.790
how could we rise again?

02:32.020 --> 02:32.860
And how could you

02:33.270 --> 02:34.740
ever become

02:35.110 --> 02:36.300
the Young Priest?

02:36.300 --> 02:37.140
Father,

02:37.900 --> 02:39.550
rising again was your wish,

02:40.180 --> 02:41.020
not mine

02:41.460 --> 02:42.860
or my siblings'.

02:43.780 --> 02:44.620
Since you

02:44.620 --> 02:45.510
have betrayed Cangshen,

02:46.620 --> 02:47.790
I should resign in shame

02:48.620 --> 02:49.680
and leave the Royal Court.

02:52.390 --> 02:53.460
How could you say that?

02:54.180 --> 02:55.300
Nonsense?

02:55.900 --> 02:56.740
Resign?

02:58.070 --> 02:59.390
Did your siblings

02:59.550 --> 03:00.620
die for nothing?

03:00.620 --> 03:02.350
Their deaths were not because of me.

03:02.990 --> 03:04.140
They died because of you.

03:05.390 --> 03:06.230
Master Yili'er,

03:07.230 --> 03:08.620
you say Luda rose this far

03:09.350 --> 03:10.990
because you dealt with an evil spirit.

03:11.860 --> 03:12.700
I don't think so.

03:13.900 --> 03:15.340
Perhaps it was the other way around.

03:16.180 --> 03:17.510
Maybe Song Xingyu saw long ago

03:17.510 --> 03:18.460
how insatiable you were

03:20.390 --> 03:21.799
and how you tried to make your son

03:21.810 --> 03:22.460
the High Priest.

03:23.020 --> 03:24.140
So, he used you.

03:37.950 --> 03:39.020
If that is true,

03:40.230 --> 03:41.180
then did I

03:42.110 --> 03:43.420
kill my own kids

03:45.350 --> 03:46.740
with my own hands?

03:54.230 --> 03:55.180
If there's nothing else,

03:55.830 --> 03:57.110
I will go back and rest first.

03:59.270 --> 04:00.580
This late-night spectacle

04:01.230 --> 04:02.270
has truly wearied me.

04:03.830 --> 04:05.860
My kids...

04:23.670 --> 04:24.510
Have you heard?

04:24.910 --> 04:26.740
Last night, at the House of Yili'er,

04:26.740 --> 04:27.670
all their treasures

04:27.910 --> 04:29.380
vanished overnight.

04:30.710 --> 04:31.820
What a pity.

04:32.110 --> 04:32.950
Indeed.

04:33.090 --> 04:33.940
By morning,

04:33.940 --> 04:35.300
the concubines and servants

04:35.500 --> 04:36.820
- Gentlemen.
- had all left.

04:37.260 --> 04:38.230
Now,

04:38.380 --> 04:39.500
only Master Yili'er

04:39.500 --> 04:40.653
and Young Master Luda remain.

04:41.180 --> 04:42.260
The other Young Master

04:42.740 --> 04:43.940
also drowned.

04:52.180 --> 04:53.420
I spoke with Father last night.

04:55.180 --> 04:56.030
He will return with me

04:56.030 --> 04:57.003
to the Capital to atone.

04:57.910 --> 04:59.260
He will never return to Youzhou.

05:01.420 --> 05:02.670
You trust Cangshen that much?

05:03.380 --> 05:04.220
Cangshen

05:04.470 --> 05:05.740
is, in truth, a kind of faith.

05:09.110 --> 05:10.230
You have convictions too.

05:11.150 --> 05:11.990
You should know this.

05:12.710 --> 05:14.030
When one's faith is firm enough,

05:14.360 --> 05:15.230
it can rival

05:15.230 --> 05:16.350
all the weapons in the world.

05:17.260 --> 05:18.100
The power of Cangshen

05:18.550 --> 05:20.120
lies in one faith shared by millions.

05:24.790 --> 05:25.630
Seventeen,

05:26.710 --> 05:27.433
you once believed

05:27.444 --> 05:28.573
in the Aphorisms of Cangshen.

05:29.260 --> 05:30.110
Why now...

05:30.110 --> 05:30.950
In the Aphorisms,

05:31.316 --> 05:32.429
Cangshen's greatest blessing

05:32.977 --> 05:34.403
is to spread the Chong People's line

05:34.820 --> 05:36.300
to every corner of the world.

05:37.060 --> 05:38.740
You marched south and seized

05:39.253 --> 05:40.633
Great Liang's land and its people.

05:41.740 --> 05:43.380
Is this what your faith asks of you?

05:48.500 --> 05:49.990
I know that between the two nations

05:50.500 --> 05:51.690
lies deep hatred.

05:52.180 --> 05:53.020
But I hope

05:53.470 --> 05:54.420
more of the Liang People

05:54.420 --> 05:55.600
will come to worship Cangshen

05:55.837 --> 05:56.986
and become Cangshen's people.

05:57.910 --> 05:59.110
Each should do their own part,

05:59.710 --> 06:00.590
with no more strife.

06:03.670 --> 06:04.510
Seventeen,

06:05.060 --> 06:06.030
have you ever wondered

06:06.910 --> 06:08.150
how I knew you last night?

06:09.860 --> 06:10.700
Young Priest,

06:12.550 --> 06:13.620
we were never friends.

06:14.790 --> 06:16.150
One day, we may be foes.

06:16.940 --> 06:17.780
So,

06:18.150 --> 06:18.990
let's part here.

06:20.230 --> 06:21.110
Take care of yourself.

06:59.790 --> 07:00.810
Greetings, Your Lordship.

07:02.260 --> 07:03.180
You hurried back.

07:03.180 --> 07:04.426
Anything wrong with Her Grace?

07:04.790 --> 07:05.740
Your Lordship,

07:05.740 --> 07:07.033
Song Xingyu was seen in Youzhou.

07:08.790 --> 07:10.110
So, Her Grace went to Youzhou

07:10.550 --> 07:11.670
because of him.

07:14.710 --> 07:16.420
Did Her Grace catch Song Xingyu?

07:16.910 --> 07:17.750
He got away.

07:19.670 --> 07:20.510
Understood.

07:20.860 --> 07:21.700
Your Lordship,

07:22.620 --> 07:23.670
there is also a spirit

07:23.670 --> 07:24.520
by her side.

07:24.530 --> 07:25.503
His identity is unknown.

07:26.030 --> 07:28.030
Are you sure it's not a mortal?

07:28.190 --> 07:29.060
It is a spirit

07:29.060 --> 07:30.046
with strong spirit power.

07:38.280 --> 07:39.460
Naan!

07:52.940 --> 07:53.780
Put me down.

07:55.060 --> 07:56.230
Tell me where Song Xingyu is,

07:56.500 --> 07:57.340
and I'll let you go.

07:58.030 --> 07:58.910
I don't know.

07:58.910 --> 07:59.860
I truly don't know.

08:00.940 --> 08:02.150
I believe you don't know.

08:02.710 --> 08:03.710
But the Sovereign won't.

08:07.710 --> 08:09.300
Fine, I'll talk.

08:10.060 --> 08:11.550
Put me down first.

08:34.140 --> 08:34.980
You...

08:49.710 --> 08:51.110
Greetings, Your Lordship.

08:51.310 --> 08:53.260
Why are you in such a panic?

08:54.430 --> 08:55.380
Your Lordship,

08:55.860 --> 08:57.430
while I was on law enforcement duty,

08:57.590 --> 08:59.740
I ran into Song Xingyu.

09:00.110 --> 09:01.310
I did all I could

09:01.740 --> 09:02.890
to stop Song Xingyu,

09:02.890 --> 09:04.140
but he still got away.

09:05.400 --> 09:06.260
I was anxious

09:06.260 --> 09:08.190
because…

09:08.620 --> 09:09.540
Because I wanted

09:09.540 --> 09:10.660
to report this news

09:10.830 --> 09:11.670
to you at once.

09:15.990 --> 09:16.830
Please believe me.

09:17.070 --> 09:17.950
These...

09:17.950 --> 09:18.790
I got

09:18.900 --> 09:19.740
these things

09:19.750 --> 09:21.110
from Song Xingyu's hideout.

09:21.430 --> 09:22.380
Please accept it.

09:22.740 --> 09:24.190
Please believe me.

09:32.990 --> 09:34.230
Kneel. Hurry.

09:34.430 --> 09:35.270
Kneel, now.

09:38.350 --> 09:39.190
Kneel.

09:40.070 --> 09:40.910
Kneel, now.

09:41.230 --> 09:42.310
Greet the Right Hand.

09:42.470 --> 09:43.310
Quickly.

09:50.350 --> 09:51.350
Please forgive him.

09:51.740 --> 09:53.310
He is a newly formed spirit.

09:53.540 --> 09:54.500
He's still confused,

09:54.500 --> 09:55.430
unaware of the rules.

09:55.430 --> 09:56.270
He...

10:06.140 --> 10:07.070
(The Right Hand?)

10:07.660 --> 10:08.860
(Is he Simu's subordinate?)

10:19.830 --> 10:20.843
Farewell, Your Lordship.

10:27.190 --> 10:28.443
Every time I see the Right Hand,

10:28.950 --> 10:29.790
it drains away

10:30.230 --> 10:31.500
ten years of joy I've saved up.

10:31.950 --> 10:32.790
How dare you

10:33.230 --> 10:34.310
look at the Right Hand?

10:34.590 --> 10:35.430
Is the Right Hand

10:36.140 --> 10:37.190
really that important?

10:37.590 --> 10:38.540
Of course.

10:39.830 --> 10:40.950
He's only inferior

10:40.950 --> 10:41.790
to Her Grace.

10:41.950 --> 10:43.310
He's the most trustworthy

10:43.310 --> 10:44.230
to Her Grace.

10:47.230 --> 10:48.230
The most trustworthy.

10:51.230 --> 10:52.070
He's known

10:52.260 --> 10:53.860
Her Grace for centuries.

10:53.860 --> 10:54.710
Those two

10:54.710 --> 10:55.990
rely on and respect

10:55.990 --> 10:56.830
each other;

10:56.830 --> 10:58.380
their hearts beat in unison.

10:58.620 --> 10:59.460
As the saying goes,

10:59.710 --> 11:01.110
their bond runs deep.

11:02.690 --> 11:03.530
In the Void,

11:03.530 --> 11:04.390
all spirits think

11:04.400 --> 11:05.410
they're a pair.

11:05.430 --> 11:06.270
For all these years,

11:06.470 --> 11:07.752
while Her Grace was away,

11:07.763 --> 11:08.830
the Right Hand handled

11:09.190 --> 11:10.540
the Spirit World like a co-ruler.

11:11.140 --> 11:12.620
Even the Left Hand lacked that honor.

11:13.190 --> 11:14.990
The Right Hand truly is a model

11:14.990 --> 11:15.830
for all male spirits.

11:17.350 --> 11:18.190
From the sound of it,

11:19.310 --> 11:21.123
the Right Hand and Her Grace
are quite close.

11:22.260 --> 11:23.260
Does Her Grace like him?

11:25.590 --> 11:26.620
Of course.

11:27.070 --> 11:28.260
The Right Hand is handsome,

11:28.430 --> 11:29.270
highly capable,

11:29.430 --> 11:30.780
and utterly devoted to her.

11:30.950 --> 11:32.230
She fell for him long ago.

11:32.500 --> 11:34.110
Otherwise, why would she trust him

11:34.350 --> 11:35.900
with the Void?

11:39.020 --> 11:39.860
If that's the case,

11:40.900 --> 11:42.070
the Right Hand is trouble.

11:42.350 --> 11:43.190
Yes, yes.

11:43.190 --> 11:44.140
He is hard to handle.

11:44.380 --> 11:45.230
If you go to the Void,

11:45.230 --> 11:46.350
don't anger him.

11:46.520 --> 11:47.390
Or you'll end up

11:47.390 --> 11:48.500
being annihilated.

11:50.950 --> 11:51.790
That is not right.

11:52.470 --> 11:54.110
You threw me off track.

11:54.710 --> 11:55.780
Why are you asking so much?

11:56.540 --> 11:57.380
Come on.

11:57.540 --> 11:59.260
I don't know where Song Xingyu is.

11:59.710 --> 12:00.620
But

12:00.620 --> 12:01.900
you need to follow me

12:02.140 --> 12:03.190
back to the Void.

12:08.070 --> 12:08.910
What?

12:14.060 --> 12:16.860
(Fragrance)

12:16.860 --> 12:21.700
(Wine)

12:30.430 --> 12:31.740
Why did you leave alone?

12:32.620 --> 12:33.740
You didn't even wait for me.

12:40.230 --> 12:41.620
Don't overdrink today.

12:42.350 --> 12:43.190
Last time…

12:43.350 --> 12:44.470
Once my spirit power is back,

12:44.860 --> 12:46.140
I will make you suffer for it.

12:49.060 --> 12:49.900
I've suffered enough

12:49.900 --> 12:50.830
in the Mortal World.

12:51.590 --> 12:52.430
It seems

12:52.810 --> 12:53.660
you'll have me sample

12:53.660 --> 12:54.500
the Void's suffering.

12:57.380 --> 12:58.740
If you insist on punishing me,

13:00.660 --> 13:01.830
let me use this

13:03.430 --> 13:04.270
to make amends.

13:12.230 --> 13:13.165
You had no five senses

13:13.176 --> 13:13.910
on the city wall.

13:14.590 --> 13:15.583
Things are different now.

13:16.660 --> 13:17.710
Though you can't taste it,

13:18.540 --> 13:19.830
you can smell its fragrance.

13:30.990 --> 13:32.500
Not enough to spare your punishment.

13:35.830 --> 13:37.110
Then you should think

13:37.620 --> 13:38.620
about how to punish me.

14:03.140 --> 14:04.710
It does seem too sweet.

14:07.350 --> 14:08.710
I have a sweet tooth too.

14:18.990 --> 14:19.830
Simu,

14:20.020 --> 14:21.660
do you want a taste of sweetness?

14:23.430 --> 14:24.900
Why not trade our five senses now?

14:27.990 --> 14:29.500
The joys of this world fade too fast.

14:29.710 --> 14:30.550
Better not be greedy.

14:31.020 --> 14:32.620
To hold one at this moment is enough.

14:38.310 --> 14:39.150
You can

14:39.470 --> 14:40.500
keep me by your side.

14:41.070 --> 14:42.110
You can exchange them

14:43.070 --> 14:43.990
whenever you want.

14:46.230 --> 14:47.070
Or,

14:47.900 --> 14:48.950
come back to Nandu with me.

14:50.740 --> 14:52.710
The food, wine, and views there

14:53.260 --> 14:54.380
will surely please you.

14:58.990 --> 14:59.830
We'll see.

15:42.230 --> 15:43.070
Great Ancestor,

15:43.260 --> 15:44.480
I've searched all of Youzhou.

15:44.620 --> 15:45.860
No trace of Song Xingyu.

15:46.190 --> 15:47.110
He truly fled.

15:47.430 --> 15:49.660
Then how can we find him now?

15:50.190 --> 15:52.190
Handle your own duty yourself.

15:52.540 --> 15:53.660
He has the Glazed Pagoda.

15:53.660 --> 15:55.140
It hides the evil spirit's aura.

15:55.500 --> 15:56.340
Do spirits

15:56.740 --> 15:57.780
have nothing

15:57.780 --> 15:58.660
that can restrain him?

15:59.540 --> 16:00.990
If spirits had a way,

16:01.116 --> 16:02.138
he wouldn't have been able

16:02.149 --> 16:03.099
to hide for 300 years.

16:03.660 --> 16:04.840
Starhaven's magical artifacts

16:04.860 --> 16:05.700
are most formidable.

16:06.310 --> 16:07.830
Yet you can't counter the Pagoda.

16:12.020 --> 16:12.860
Great Ancestor,

16:13.380 --> 16:15.500
why not come to Nandu?

16:16.190 --> 16:17.110
We can work out

16:17.110 --> 16:18.190
how to catch Song Xingyu.

16:20.260 --> 16:22.500
It has been so long since I saw you.

16:22.500 --> 16:23.950
You finally have official leave.

16:23.950 --> 16:25.140
Come to Nandu, okay?

16:26.860 --> 16:28.310
Your spell bearer, Duan Xu,

16:28.900 --> 16:30.380
is also returning to Nandu.

16:33.230 --> 16:34.950
A mortal life is brief.

16:35.310 --> 16:36.230
Perhaps,

16:36.230 --> 16:37.660
by your next official leave,

16:37.830 --> 16:38.670
he…

16:40.140 --> 16:41.780
He may already be gone.

16:43.070 --> 16:44.230
You should come to Nandu

16:44.380 --> 16:45.500
and truly enjoy yourself

16:45.740 --> 16:46.860
by changing your five senses.

16:50.860 --> 16:52.070
That sounds like a fair idea.

16:52.990 --> 16:53.830
I will think it over.

16:55.070 --> 16:55.910
I...

17:14.300 --> 17:17.460
(East Sea, Fusang Tree)

17:52.540 --> 17:53.380
What is going on?

17:53.820 --> 17:55.340
Why did the Fusang Tree wither?

17:56.020 --> 17:57.346
Wars in the Mortal World rage on.

17:57.500 --> 17:58.910
The Fusang Tree bore it long.

17:59.190 --> 18:00.643
Perhaps the strain finally took hold.

18:02.020 --> 18:03.300
You're responsible

18:03.300 --> 18:05.150
for its yearly upkeep.

18:05.780 --> 18:07.820
How did things worsen so suddenly?

18:10.260 --> 18:11.540
Question me

18:11.710 --> 18:12.580
after pointing out

18:12.580 --> 18:14.580
where I was at fault.

18:16.260 --> 18:18.100
If a spirit was meddling within,

18:18.340 --> 18:20.580
you oversee the access
of the Spirit Officials.

18:20.910 --> 18:22.950
Maybe you're responsible for this.

18:27.670 --> 18:28.510
Oh, no.

18:56.776 --> 18:57.815
The Fusang Tree has split.

18:58.470 --> 19:00.020
We're not powerful enough to repair it.

19:00.430 --> 19:01.870
We must ask Her Grace to come.

19:02.820 --> 19:04.500
Her Grace must have sensed it.

19:04.670 --> 19:05.950
I'll go to receive her.

19:22.950 --> 19:24.300
Rare for you to ask me out.

19:25.540 --> 19:26.500
On my way here,

19:26.500 --> 19:27.870
I saw these rare wildflowers.

19:28.580 --> 19:29.470
Smell them.

19:43.020 --> 19:44.500
Once the exchange of senses is over,

19:45.870 --> 19:47.100
I will return to the Void.

19:55.670 --> 19:56.510
Your Grace,

19:59.340 --> 20:00.180
you truly don't mean

20:01.710 --> 20:02.990
to return to Nandu with me?

20:06.430 --> 20:07.430
Nandu is merely

20:07.430 --> 20:08.430
a city of mortals.

20:09.740 --> 20:11.060
During my next official leave,

20:12.060 --> 20:13.230
I can go and see it.

20:16.340 --> 20:19.980
♪Joys and sorrows of the mortal world♪

20:19.980 --> 20:22.890
♪Swept along by the daylight♪

20:22.910 --> 20:24.100
Next time you come,

20:25.780 --> 20:26.820
I may no longer be here.

20:28.260 --> 20:30.940
♪Lingering for a fleeting moment♪

20:31.100 --> 20:35.420
♪Was once touched by laughing tears♪

20:37.670 --> 20:38.740
Then do your best

20:38.740 --> 20:39.580
to stay alive.

20:39.620 --> 20:44.700
♪I'd be a guest in a sweet dream♪

20:46.820 --> 20:50.300
♪Dawn and dusk rise and set♪

20:50.580 --> 20:54.100
♪Longing to meet, yet parted by destiny♪

20:54.620 --> 20:58.220
♪Let me wander through♪

20:58.220 --> 21:01.860
♪Light and dark, without turning back♪

21:02.260 --> 21:05.660
♪Wander to the other shore
with the lantern♪

21:05.820 --> 21:09.820
♪Accompanied by eternity♪

21:10.020 --> 21:12.700
♪As all things turn and flow♪

21:12.820 --> 21:17.520
♪Whether I stay or go, I'm all alone♪

21:17.520 --> 21:21.000
♪Dawn and dusk rise and set♪

21:21.280 --> 21:24.800
♪Longing to meet, yet parted by destiny♪

21:25.320 --> 21:28.920
♪Let me wander through♪

21:28.920 --> 21:31.800
♪Light and dark, without turning back♪

21:31.820 --> 21:32.660
The time has come.

21:32.960 --> 21:36.360
♪Wander to the other shore
with the lantern♪

21:37.950 --> 21:39.300
I didn't expect ten days

21:41.910 --> 21:42.870
to pass by so quickly.

21:43.520 --> 21:49.480
♪Whether I stay or go, I'm all alone♪

22:03.620 --> 22:07.140
♪As stars shift and change places♪

22:07.360 --> 22:10.970
♪A century is like a dream♪

22:11.360 --> 22:14.750
♪Let me journey across them all♪

22:14.890 --> 22:18.480
♪Without reincarnations♪

22:18.740 --> 22:19.580
Your eyes

22:19.600 --> 22:20.870
can still see spirits.

22:22.390 --> 22:23.670
Consider it a gift

22:24.540 --> 22:26.100
for letting me know

22:26.500 --> 22:27.340
what scent is

22:27.870 --> 22:28.910
and what touch feels like.

22:31.340 --> 22:32.260
This is where we part.

22:34.430 --> 22:35.430
Remember to stay alive.

23:24.910 --> 23:25.750
Your Grace.

23:41.500 --> 23:42.340
Simu.

23:44.340 --> 23:45.180
Simu.

23:47.580 --> 23:48.500
The game is over.

23:49.870 --> 23:50.710
Go back.

23:51.430 --> 23:52.540
Return to your Nandu.

23:53.190 --> 23:54.030
What about you?

23:55.020 --> 23:56.100
You're rushing back.

23:56.910 --> 23:57.750
Why?

23:59.100 --> 24:00.580
None of your concern.

24:07.230 --> 24:08.950
If you take me with you,

24:09.740 --> 24:10.820
it'll concern me.

24:15.100 --> 24:15.940
Why should I?

24:22.150 --> 24:23.190
You'll leave for years.

24:24.470 --> 24:25.670
Next time you come,

24:26.580 --> 24:27.540
I may have died.

24:28.630 --> 24:29.500
Wouldn't that waste

24:29.500 --> 24:30.340
our spell bond?

24:34.700 --> 24:35.960
I was reckless before.

24:36.390 --> 24:37.600
I offended you more than once.

24:39.100 --> 24:40.740
Will you truly let me off so easily?

24:42.580 --> 24:43.569
Don't you want to settle

24:43.580 --> 24:44.540
the score with me

24:45.580 --> 24:46.580
and make me pay?

24:49.100 --> 24:49.980
In this bargain,

24:51.020 --> 24:52.180
you still owe me one wish.

24:53.780 --> 24:54.620
This time, my wish

24:55.592 --> 24:56.931
is to return to the Void with you.

25:12.460 --> 25:13.420
Do you know the price

25:13.420 --> 25:14.700
to enter the Void

25:15.500 --> 25:16.380
as a mortal?

25:24.060 --> 25:24.900
A true gambler

25:26.060 --> 25:26.853
does not gamble

25:26.864 --> 25:27.957
before knowing the result.

25:28.820 --> 25:30.180
Entering the Void

25:31.260 --> 25:32.180
is more dreadful

25:33.460 --> 25:34.500
than death to mortals.

25:36.140 --> 25:36.980
So what?

25:59.380 --> 26:00.780
So, this is the famed

26:02.060 --> 26:03.220
Fusang Tree of the Cyan Sea.

26:05.380 --> 26:06.420
Mortals can never reach

26:06.580 --> 26:07.940
the Cyan Sea's depths.

26:08.700 --> 26:10.060
If you rush in carelessly,

26:10.340 --> 26:11.780
you will lose your life.

26:24.620 --> 26:25.940
The Fusang Tree

26:26.180 --> 26:27.260
has withered more.

26:52.860 --> 26:54.540
For now, I can only restore its surface.

26:55.540 --> 26:56.740
To fully heal it,

26:57.140 --> 26:58.100
it will take more time.

27:13.460 --> 27:14.740
If you want to enter the Void,

27:15.740 --> 27:16.820
jump down from here.

27:17.940 --> 27:19.260
Think it through first.

27:21.060 --> 27:22.660
The upward force

27:22.780 --> 27:24.160
of the countless Spirit Auras below

27:24.726 --> 27:25.660
is enough to tear apart

27:25.660 --> 27:26.980
your mortal flesh.

27:28.540 --> 27:30.260
You can regret it now.

27:32.620 --> 27:33.860
This kind of makeshift shortcut

27:34.020 --> 27:35.900
can let a mortal pass through,

27:35.900 --> 27:37.180
but it's extremely dangerous.

27:38.020 --> 27:38.860
Young man,

27:39.020 --> 27:40.180
I advise you not to try it.

27:40.580 --> 27:41.860
Just go back to the Mortal World.

27:43.940 --> 27:45.060
It does look frightening,

27:46.420 --> 27:47.500
but I've come this far.

27:48.140 --> 27:49.300
I have no reason to turn back.

27:51.460 --> 27:52.620
To read the moment

27:53.220 --> 27:54.180
and adapt is

27:55.060 --> 27:55.940
the right thing to do

27:55.940 --> 27:57.060
for a mortal.

27:59.940 --> 28:00.780
You're right.

28:02.460 --> 28:04.060
But you refused to go to Nandu.

28:05.220 --> 28:06.460
So, I have to come to the Void.

28:07.180 --> 28:13.040
♪Touched memories linger like shadows♪

28:13.670 --> 28:19.180
♪Scattered reflections
sink into my heart♪

28:19.770 --> 28:25.780
♪If I could softly call you like this♪

28:26.870 --> 28:31.480
♪As gentle as a fleeting embrace♪

28:32.980 --> 28:38.630
♪Though apart, my thoughts still swirl♪

28:39.250 --> 28:44.870
♪A lifetime is given
for a name to be remembered♪

28:45.400 --> 28:48.760
♪There are passions and pains♪

28:48.960 --> 28:51.860
♪Hope we'll experience them together♪

28:52.540 --> 28:58.770
♪Before we forget or grow apart♪

29:00.080 --> 29:02.840
♪Even if the day gives way to night♪

29:02.840 --> 29:04.490
♪Grows dim and fades away♪

29:04.490 --> 29:07.320
♪What would come of it?♪

29:07.730 --> 29:09.230
♪I care for no one but you♪

29:09.230 --> 29:10.880
♪I'll come near and run to you♪

29:10.940 --> 29:12.540
Your Grace, if you can't help him,

29:13.140 --> 29:14.500
I can go and save him.

29:14.580 --> 29:17.270
♪Miracles, eternity, and radiance♪

29:17.270 --> 29:20.020
♪Worth more than any barren land♪

29:20.260 --> 29:22.620
♪I might as well
spend the rest of my life♪

29:22.620 --> 29:26.590
♪Walking with you through eternity♪

29:43.540 --> 29:45.700
That mortal can actually descend?

29:46.980 --> 29:48.340
I wonder if it's because

29:48.460 --> 29:50.260
of the weakened Fusang Tree

29:50.900 --> 29:52.860
or his sword.

29:53.460 --> 29:54.860
He actually passed.

30:02.660 --> 30:04.700
Your Grace, let us enter the Void.

31:56.940 --> 32:03.940
(Sovereign's Hall)

32:49.220 --> 32:54.240
♪Spirits are intoxicated♪

32:54.240 --> 32:58.360
♪With obsessions♪

32:59.620 --> 33:02.660
Your Grace, welcome back.

33:03.100 --> 33:06.060
Your Grace, welcome back.

33:12.180 --> 33:17.750
♪Today, a home is granted♪

33:18.000 --> 33:23.150
♪Joy without grief♪

33:23.820 --> 33:28.750
♪Lanterns light the empty delusions♪

33:28.890 --> 33:33.570
♪All are ferried across♪

34:10.220 --> 34:15.070
♪Spirits are intoxicated♪

34:15.240 --> 34:18.890
♪With obsessions♪

34:21.670 --> 34:26.620
♪Forget the form to achieve♪

34:26.840 --> 34:30.790
♪Yet I can't♪

34:33.360 --> 34:37.580
♪Today, a home is granted♪

34:37.580 --> 34:39.040
(Sovereign's Hall)

34:39.040 --> 34:44.180
♪Joy without grief♪

34:44.860 --> 34:49.900
♪Lanterns light the empty delusions♪

34:49.900 --> 34:54.460
♪All are ferried across♪

35:38.940 --> 35:39.860
(It's him.)

35:53.780 --> 35:55.250
Seize this mortal and drag him away.

35:55.303 --> 35:56.250
Hang him for three days.

35:56.250 --> 35:57.100
Yes, Your Grace.

35:57.100 --> 35:58.620
You've come for me at last.

36:08.500 --> 36:09.340
Up.

36:11.580 --> 36:12.660
What is that mortal

36:13.060 --> 36:14.380
hanging there to Her Grace?

36:14.580 --> 36:15.606
He must've enraged her

36:15.617 --> 36:16.820
by committing the gravest sin.

36:18.500 --> 36:19.500
He looks so tender.

36:19.900 --> 36:20.740
I wonder whom

36:21.060 --> 36:22.179
Her Grace will grant him to.

36:23.780 --> 36:24.860
Tender and delicious.

36:25.940 --> 36:26.900
I really want a bite.

36:28.740 --> 36:29.740
Higher. A little higher.

37:06.500 --> 37:07.826
The Sovereign's Hall of the Void.

37:29.820 --> 37:30.660
Your Grace,

37:30.940 --> 37:31.993
the Fusang Tree has split,

37:32.140 --> 37:33.500
and many evil spirits fled at once.

37:33.693 --> 37:34.889
(Lei Qi,)
Lords have sent

37:34.900 --> 37:36.180
(Lord of Zhuangling Temple)
Spirit Officials to arrest them,

37:36.180 --> 37:37.100
but there are too many.

37:37.460 --> 37:38.700
Your Grace, please send more,

37:38.820 --> 37:40.500
lest evil spirits
plague the Mortal World.

37:40.860 --> 37:41.700
Indeed.

37:42.580 --> 37:44.340
Every temple is deeply unsettled,

37:45.820 --> 37:47.246
for fear that chaos may break out.

37:48.620 --> 37:50.020
What trouble could there be?

37:51.860 --> 37:54.220
Since the evil spirits reached
the Mortal World,

37:54.340 --> 37:56.460
let Starhaven Sect deal with them.

37:57.100 --> 37:59.020
They've had it easy for centuries;

37:59.260 --> 38:01.460
it's time they toughened up a bit.

38:02.060 --> 38:03.460
Send more?

38:03.860 --> 38:05.500
That would waste many spirit stones.

38:06.620 --> 38:07.740
Matters of our Spirit World

38:07.740 --> 38:09.460
should not be left to outsiders.

38:11.220 --> 38:12.620
I've ordered Lords to sort out

38:12.780 --> 38:14.660
the list of escaped evil spirits.

38:15.300 --> 38:16.613
The Spirit Officials we sent out

38:16.660 --> 38:18.220
have brought back over 60%.

38:18.660 --> 38:19.500
Given some time,

38:19.820 --> 38:21.380
we can surely bring them all back.

38:22.220 --> 38:23.540
But right now, in the Void,

38:23.940 --> 38:25.940
there are too many spirits.

38:26.620 --> 38:28.500
If they are not settled properly,

38:29.100 --> 38:29.980
there could be

38:30.140 --> 38:31.940
chaos from evil spirits clashing.

38:32.660 --> 38:33.860
If only we could make them

38:34.140 --> 38:36.260
vanish in a proper manner.

38:40.660 --> 38:41.740
We have the Ascension Pool,

38:42.140 --> 38:42.980
right?

38:43.940 --> 38:45.860
It's lain unused

38:46.060 --> 38:47.349
(Dong Yong,)
because spirits

38:47.360 --> 38:48.380
(Lord of Yuling Temple)
are bound by obsessions

38:48.660 --> 38:50.100
too deep to ascend.

38:50.820 --> 38:52.220
- Indeed.
- Exactly.

38:53.100 --> 38:53.980
Your Grace,

38:54.660 --> 38:56.260
to the northwest lies North Abyss.

38:56.700 --> 38:57.660
The land there is vast,

38:58.300 --> 38:59.660
with hidden spirit stones.

39:00.220 --> 39:01.313
If we can open that region,

39:01.820 --> 39:02.860
it would house

39:03.020 --> 39:03.860
the spirits

39:04.500 --> 39:07.620
and also expand the Void's domain.

39:09.610 --> 39:11.620
We risked our lives

39:11.620 --> 39:12.500
to build the Void.

39:12.900 --> 39:13.740
The 24 Temples

39:13.980 --> 39:14.900
spent a thousand years

39:14.900 --> 39:15.900
regaining their strength.

39:16.140 --> 39:17.660
Peace has only just returned,

39:17.660 --> 39:19.020
and now, we must risk all again?

39:22.220 --> 39:25.780
North Abyss often has seabed storms.

39:26.260 --> 39:28.020
For ordinary spirits to go near it

39:28.180 --> 39:29.860
is nearly certain death.

39:30.180 --> 39:31.940
Rather than waste wealth
and spirit power,

39:32.100 --> 39:33.020
I believe

39:33.020 --> 39:34.940
we should expand the dwellings nearby

39:35.260 --> 39:36.820
to ease the urgent need.

39:37.540 --> 39:38.380
Indeed.

39:38.380 --> 39:39.460
That is a fine plan.

39:39.820 --> 39:40.780
Indeed.

39:42.100 --> 39:42.940
Starting today,

39:43.780 --> 39:45.540
all spirits entering the Void

39:45.940 --> 39:47.460
shall be registered by the Right Hand.

39:47.940 --> 39:48.940
The other Lords

39:49.380 --> 39:50.980
shall help expand the dwellings

39:51.380 --> 39:52.300
to house them.

39:53.140 --> 39:54.820
As for opening the North Abyss,

39:55.500 --> 39:56.900
the Left and Right Hands

39:57.460 --> 39:58.820
shall draft the rules for me first.

39:59.620 --> 40:00.660
In the 24 Temples,

40:01.500 --> 40:03.740
if any can persuade spirits to ascend,

40:04.300 --> 40:05.580
for each spirit that ascends,

40:06.140 --> 40:07.500
the reward is 30,000 spirit stones.

40:08.820 --> 40:09.700
How much? 30,000?

40:09.700 --> 40:10.540
30,000 spirit stones.

40:10.740 --> 40:11.700
- That many?
- 30,000.

40:12.060 --> 40:13.140
No upper limit.

40:23.140 --> 40:23.980
Your Grace,

40:24.900 --> 40:26.850
Fang Chang colluded with Song Xingyu.

40:27.140 --> 40:28.600
Though Fang Chang is now in custody,

40:28.780 --> 40:30.850
Song Xingyu is still at large.

40:31.260 --> 40:32.290
Your Grace, please,

40:32.300 --> 40:34.260
(Yan Zhang,)
deal with this first.

40:34.500 --> 40:36.620
(Vice Lord of Xuling Temple)
Song Xingyu's crimes merit no pardon.

40:37.340 --> 40:39.180
I have sent men to hunt him down.

40:41.740 --> 40:43.300
Fang Chang has been seized by me.

40:43.820 --> 40:45.340
Your Grace, I await your judgment.

40:48.180 --> 40:50.100
The Right Hand did well

40:51.380 --> 40:52.630
in capturing Fang Chang.

40:53.940 --> 40:55.990
Fang Chang deserves to be annihilated

40:56.380 --> 40:58.700
before the Golden-wall Decrees
in three days.

40:59.340 --> 41:00.900
Guan Huai failed in oversight.

41:01.300 --> 41:02.220
Shave his head.

41:02.380 --> 41:03.820
Imprison him for ten years.

41:04.180 --> 41:05.060
During that time,

41:05.060 --> 41:06.300
the Left Hand is

41:06.340 --> 41:07.686
in charge of the Shanling Temple.

41:08.020 --> 41:09.260
Your Grace, you must not.

41:09.420 --> 41:10.486
Your Grace, you must not!

41:10.900 --> 41:12.080
A spirit's hair,

41:12.100 --> 41:14.220
once cut, will never grow back.

41:14.580 --> 41:15.860
If you cut my hair,

41:15.860 --> 41:17.640
you're taking my life.

41:18.180 --> 41:19.340
Then cut only half.

41:20.020 --> 41:21.540
Not even half will do.

41:21.980 --> 41:23.220
Your Grace, you must not.

41:23.220 --> 41:24.060
Your Grace.

41:24.940 --> 41:26.260
Your Grace, you must not.

41:26.490 --> 41:27.960
Your Grace, you must not!

41:29.660 --> 41:30.500
Your Grace!

41:30.940 --> 41:32.300
Fang Chang kept saying

41:32.300 --> 41:34.000
he would avenge Shao Yinyin,

41:34.340 --> 41:35.850
but in truth, for his career,

41:35.860 --> 41:37.240
he killed her with his own hands.

41:37.870 --> 41:38.940
A heartless man like that

41:38.940 --> 41:40.230
toyed with a woman's feelings.

41:40.380 --> 41:41.860
That is sheer hypocrisy.

41:42.940 --> 41:43.780
Why not

41:44.100 --> 41:45.520
send him to my hall

41:45.530 --> 41:46.760
before his execution?

41:47.720 --> 41:49.090
The ladies in my hall

41:49.380 --> 41:50.260
are fond of tending

41:50.260 --> 41:51.740
to such heartless men.

41:54.180 --> 41:55.240
In these three days,

41:55.740 --> 41:56.580
I will make sure

41:56.900 --> 41:58.140
he begs for death.

42:03.140 --> 42:04.900
Yan Zhang, Vice Lord of Xuling Temple,

42:05.660 --> 42:07.220
has served me well in this plan.

42:08.140 --> 42:09.393
Reward her 10,000 spirit stones.

42:09.940 --> 42:10.860
Thank you, Your Grace.

42:15.100 --> 42:17.060
Farewell, Your Grace.

43:06.601 --> 43:11.931
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

43:12.261 --> 43:16.511
♪Light encountered shadow♪

43:17.871 --> 43:23.241
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

43:23.541 --> 43:28.141
♪The unbreakable fate♪

43:29.231 --> 43:31.071
♪Suddenly cracked♪

43:43.281 --> 43:48.721
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

43:48.901 --> 43:53.231
♪Light encountered shadow♪

43:54.601 --> 43:59.991
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

44:00.221 --> 44:04.161
♪The unbreakable fate♪

44:05.931 --> 44:07.821
♪Suddenly cracked♪

44:10.481 --> 44:13.641
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

44:13.641 --> 44:16.171
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

44:16.171 --> 44:21.691
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

44:21.691 --> 44:24.931
♪Following fate's guidance♪

44:24.931 --> 44:29.791
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

44:30.131 --> 44:33.151
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

44:33.151 --> 44:35.971
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

44:36.231 --> 44:38.761
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

44:38.761 --> 44:44.181
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

44:44.351 --> 44:47.421
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

44:47.581 --> 44:52.481
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

44:52.691 --> 44:56.161
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
